### List relationships
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/relationships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create blocked-by relationship
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/relationships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "targetCardId": "{{targetCardId}}",
  "type": 1
}

### Create relationship (duplicate failure)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/relationships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "targetCardId": "{{targetCardId}}",
  "type": 1
}

### Create relationship (cycle failure - A blocked by B, then B blocked by A)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{blockingCardId}}/relationships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "targetCardId": "{{cardId}}",
  "type": 1
}

### Create relates relationship
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/relationships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "targetCardId": "{{otherCardId}}",
  "type": 3
}

### Delete relationship
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/relationships/{{relationshipId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Archive impact (preflight without confirm)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/archive-impact
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Archive impact (preflight with confirm)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/archive-impact?confirm=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Archive with relationships (confirm)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/cards/{{cardId}}/archive-with-relationships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "confirm": true
}
